long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
******************************************************************************************************************
*** MUST BE A COLLABERA EMPLOYEE TO LOGIN AND AUTHENTICATE TO COLLABERA'S ENVIRONMENT  ***
******************************************************************************************************************
Only authenticated active Collabera employees will be able to utilize this extension. Authentication methods are maintained through active directly and syncing directly with Collabera's INTERNAL HR system.

This tool is used to verify the consultant's timesheet and project information. The authenticated active Collabera employees can reach to client portal based on their access.
